		{
			"uuid": "8eec2503-a4a7-47fb-a0a0-8ef98d6321aa",
			"title": "GAMEPLAY: Pizza Making Minigame",
			"description": "This level will be one of the ways in which the player can obtain money. The goal of the mini-game is to pick up ingredients from a specific spot in the level, putting that ingredient on the player's top side slot. \n\nPlayer needs to move somewhere inside the pizza and leave behind that ingredient wherever there is a free space. Each order will ask for a list of ingredients it wants with quantities. \n\nMechanics to make this more fun:\n\nSpicy Pepperoni - Wherever a pepperoni is placed, there is a high chance a fire will spawn on top (or maybe nearby), making it harder for the player to deal with the board unless they use balloon pop or fire extinguisher\n\n\n",
			"category": "471f5549-33af-4f98-8d7b-239df9494dcf",
			"steps": [
				{
					"details": "Pizza Cutter Sawblades",
					"done": false
				},
				{
					"details": "Ingredient Drop-off Area",
					"done": false
